## Contract test maintainer sync

When you create or modify matching files:

1. **Read** `.cursor/skills/contract-test-maintainer/SKILL.md`.
2. Update nock fixtures and matchers when external request/response shapes change.
3. Run `pnpm test:contract` before finishing (also runs in CI Quality job).
